     <body>
     <div type="poem">
   <head>Liber Lectores alloquitur.</head>
   <l>HEm! tu qui (leve paginas pererrans</l>
   <l>Nostras pollice, &amp; inquiete ocello)</l>
   <l>Piscaris rabidum tibi venenum</l>
   <l>Ex hoc fonticulo, scaturienti</l>
   <l>Nisi <hi>Castaliae</hi> liquore, nullo;</l>
   <l>Abito procul hinc: facessat ist hic</l>
   <l>Ocelli malè prurientis ardor.</l>
   <l>Non nostris olidae natant papyris</l>
   <l>
      <hi>Algae;</hi> nec levibus tume sco nugis</l>
   <l>Molestanta, scelus <hi>Patre</hi> expiandum</l>
   <l>
      <hi>Lemnio!</hi> hinc profugus <hi>Cupido</hi>: lirae,</l>
   <l>Sordes, qui squiliae exulant, &amp; omnis</l>
   <l>Putredo, iuveni nocens legenti.</l>
   <l>Quin tu, sobrie, docte, perspicacis</l>
   <l>Cui luces Aquilae, altius{que} acumen,</l>
   <l>
      <pb facs="6"/>Cultor <hi>Virginis</hi> integer <hi>Patrimae;</hi>
   </l>
   <l>Et tu, <hi>Montis</hi> amans biforme culmen</l>
   <l>Chara progenies novem Dearum,</l>
   <l>Adsis; &amp; genium, meum{que} carmen</l>
   <l>Expendas (rogo) strictiore lance</l>
   <l>Tui iudicij sagacioris.</l>
   <l>Non supercilium, striasve frontis</l>
   <l>Declino tetric as minacioris:</l>
   <l>
      <hi>Thaletem</hi> accipio; venito <hi>Brute,</hi>
   </l>
   <l>Censorem volo te; severioris</l>
   <l>Nec durum fugio <hi>Catonis</hi> vnguem.</l>
   <l>Hoc est quod fugio; labore tanto,</l>
   <l>Commentum peperisse mollicellum,</l>
   <l>Veltricas, apinasve; queis, inepto</l>
   <l>Ridendi moveatur a<gap reason="illegible" resp="#pdcc" extent="1 letter">
         <desc>•</desc>
      </gap>sa vulgo.</l>
   <signed>N. Debillus.</signed>
</div>
